snippet.title: Brandon James Greer
snippet.description: Hello There! My name's Brandon and I make pictures out of tiny squares! I love going into the technical aspects and design choices behind pixel art construction, so join me here for tutorials, timelapses, and concept-to-completion of pixel art pieces!
